  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to evaluate the quality of blunt dissection during
      abdominal and pelvic surgery involving dissection of adhesions, separation of blood vessels
      and neurovascular structures while preserving the integrity of these structures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
